high_descs: Look down at the bathroom counter.
Pick up the candle from the counter.
Move further back from the sink and look down at the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door on the right, put the candle inside of the cabinet, and close the door.
Walk to the sink on the right side of the counter.
Pick up the candle that's on the right.
Move further back from the sink and look down at the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door on the right, place the candle inside of the cabinet to the right of the other candle, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two candles to the cabinet.

high_descs: Take a step back from the sink
Pick up the candle from the counter between the two sinks
Turn all-way around to face the sink cabinet
Open the rightmost drawer, put the candle inside, and close it
Turn around to face the rightmost sink
Pick up the right side candle next to the sink
Turn all the way around to face the same drawer
Open the drawer, place the second candle inside it, and close it
anns.task_desc: Place two candles inside the sink cabinet

high_descs: Look down slightly to face the counter between the sinks
Pick up the candle from the counter
Turn and walk slightly away from the counter then turn back to face it
Open the bottom right cabinet under the right sink and put the candle in it
Walk forward to the right sink
Pick up the right most candle from the counter
Turn and walk slightly away from the counter then turn back to face it
Open the bottom right cabinet under the right sink and put the candle in it
anns.task_desc: Put the candles in the cabinet
